"title": "5888: inferiority",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5888: inferiority",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A discouraging sense of being of less importance or value in comparison with others.</p>\n<h2>Inferiority as a depressing lack of self-worth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:15\">JDG 6:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:6\">PSA 22:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:3\">1CO 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:23\">1SA 18:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:4\">NEH 4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:9\">NEH 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:9-Ps31:10\">PSA 31:9–31:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps70:5\">PSA 70:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:21\">PSA 74:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:1\">PSA 86:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:22\">PSA 109:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:25\">PSA 119:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:141\">PSA 119:141</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:16\">ECC 9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:8\">ISA 33:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:28\">JER 22:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:11\">LAM 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:9\">MAL 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>Inferiority as a healthy sense of unworthiness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:5\">ISA 6:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:3\">MAT 5:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:8\">LUK 5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:13\">2SA 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:6\">JOB 42:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:1-Ps38:22\">PSA 38:1–38:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:3-Ps51:5\">PSA 51:3–51:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:17\">REV 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:17\">REV 3:17</a></p>\n<h2>God's judgment will bring inferiority on on proud nations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:2\">OBA 1:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:14\">ISA 16:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:15\">JER 49:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek29:15\">EZK 29:15</a></p>\n<h2>Refusing to be intimidated by a sense of inferiority</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:3\">JOB 12:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:12\">1TI 4:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job13:2\">JOB 13:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:5\">2CO 11:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:11\">2CO 12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:15\">TIT 2:15</a></p>\n<h2>God values those regarded as inferior and uses them</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:7-Deut7:8\">DEU 7:7–7:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:27-1Cor1:28\">1CO 1:27–1:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:8\">1SA 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:5\">PSA 12:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:6\">PSA 34:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:10\">PSA 35:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:7\">PSA 36:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:17\">PSA 40:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:13\">PSA 72:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps136:23\">PSA 136:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:12\">PSA 140:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:4\">ISA 11:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:4\">ISA 25:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:19\">ISA 29:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:14\">ISA 41:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:7\">ISA 49:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:3\">ISA 61:1–61:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1-Hos11:4\">HOS 11:1–11:4</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ valued those traditionally regarded as inferior</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:2-Matt8:4\">MAT 8:2–8:4</a> <em>the diseased and ritually unclean</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:10-Matt9:13\">MAT 9:10–9:13</a> <em>the morally unacceptable</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:21-Matt15:29\">MAT 15:21–15:29</a> <em>non-Jews</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:13-Matt19:14\">MAT 19:13–19:14</a> <em>children</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:13\">LUK 18:13</a> <em>those who are ashamed of their sins</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:9\">JHN 4:9</a> <em>women</em></p>\n<h2>Believers are to help and encourage those who feel inferior</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:13\">LUK 14:13</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:16\">ROM 12:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:3-Ps82:4\">PSA 82:3–82:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:14\">1TH 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:12-Heb12:13\">HEB 12:12–12:13</a></p>",
